Date: Mon, 30 Jun 2025 11:00:54 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] drm/tests: Fix drm_test_fb_xrgb8888_to_xrgb2101010() on
 big-endian
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1012628
